OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy early cloud will soon
OL,6,Fclear westwards to leave a largely
OL,7,Ffine day with plenty of sunny spells.
OL,8,FTemperatures will be near average,
OL,9,Fthough feeling a little cooler at
OL,10,Ftimes due to the onshore breeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FAfter a mostly clear start,
OL,13,Fsome patchy low cloud and fog may
OL,14,Fdevelop in the west, persisting
OL,15,Fthrough the night. Chilly, especially
OL,16,Fduring any more prolonged clear spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
