OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FAny patchy low cloud and
OL,6,Ffog will clear quickly to give a fine
OL,7,Fday with plenty of sunny spells.
OL,8,FFeeling breezy at times, especially
OL,9,Ftowards the coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FMainly fine in this period, however
OL,13,Fthe onshore breeze is likely to bring
OL,14,Fin areas of low cloud. Often
OL,15,Feventually brightest in the south and
OL,16,Fwest after cloudy, chilly starts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
